SUICIDE: Permanently delete your character

Syntax: suicide

DESCRIPTION:
  Permanently deletes your character. Only available to characters
  level 3 or below. You will be asked to type YES to confirm.
  Any other response cancels the command.

  Wizards cannot use suicide.

  This command is blocked while you are in combat.

  Once confirmed, your character is deleted immediately and your
  name becomes available for a new character.

NOTE:
  Characters above level 3 are permanently lost when killed with
  zero lives remaining. See 'help death'.

SEE ALSO: quit, death
